casebody.data:
Lou A. BABINEAUX
v.
The BOARD OF SUPERVISORS FOR the UNIVERSITY OF LOUISIANA SYSTEM NO. 2018-CC-1663 Supreme Court of Louisiana. January 8, 2019 ON SUPERVISORY WRIT TO THE NINETEENTH JUDICIAL DISTRICT COURT, PARISH OF EAST BATON ROUGE PER CURIAM

Granted. The case is remanded to the court of appeal for briefing, argument and full opinion, with due consideration of its earlier holding in Washington v. the Board of Supervisors for the University of Louisiana System , 2018-0008 (La. App. 1 Cir. 5/14/18), 2018 WL 2202309 .

WEIMER, J., would grant and docket.
